00:28.720 --> 00:30.040
<font color="yellow">Morning.</font>

00:35.640 --> 00:38.040
<font color="yellow">'By the time I'd been</font>
<font color="yellow">in Poplar for a year,</font>

00:38.040 --> 00:41.120
<font color="yellow">'I'd begun to see</font>
<font color="yellow">myself as rather bold.'</font>

00:41.120 --> 00:43.520
<font color="white">BICYCLE BELL RINGS</font>
<font color="cyan">Coming to examine me?!</font>

00:43.520 --> 00:46.920
<font color="yellow">'Dank alleys did not frighten me,</font>
<font color="yellow">and neither did their occupants.</font>

00:48.080 --> 00:50.200
<font color="yellow">'But did I really take risks?</font>

00:50.200 --> 00:53.960
<font color="yellow">'Did I really</font>
<font color="yellow">look beyond the surface,</font>

00:53.960 --> 00:55.960
<font color="yellow">'to the darker things beneath?</font>

00:56.960 --> 00:59.600
<font color="yellow">'My uniform was my armour.</font>

00:59.600 --> 01:03.520
<font color="yellow">'And there was much about the East</font>
<font color="yellow">End that I did not need to know.</font>

01:04.680 --> 01:07.160
<font color="yellow">'Much about life</font>
<font color="yellow">I had yet to encounter.</font>

01:07.160 --> 01:09.800
<font color="yellow">'It was a safe bet</font>

01:09.800 --> 01:12.320
<font color="yellow">'that surprises lay in store.'</font>

01:12.320 --> 01:15.080
<font color="white">Teddy boys - what a state!</font>

01:15.080 --> 01:17.600
<font color="white">I know women that spend less time</font>
<font color="white">on their hair than they do.</font>

01:17.600 --> 01:19.800
<font color="cyan">Ah, you're just jealous, Fred.</font>
<font color="white">No, I ain't.</font>

01:19.800 --> 01:21.280
<font color="white">Men are supposed to be men,</font>

01:21.280 --> 01:24.880
<font color="white">not wasting all their money</font>
<font color="white">on Brylcreem and fancy waistcoats.</font>

01:24.880 --> 01:26.320
<font color="cyan">It's, er, your go.</font>

01:27.640 --> 01:29.480
<font color="white">Ruby ready to drop?</font>

01:29.480 --> 01:31.000
<font color="cyan">She is.</font>

01:31.000 --> 01:33.520
<font color="cyan">I'll have my handsome son</font>
<font color="cyan">by the end of the month.</font>

01:33.520 --> 01:34.840
<font color="white">Oh!</font>

01:34.840 --> 01:38.200
<font color="white">Turned into one of those</font>
<font color="white">clairvoyants, have you, Dougie?</font>

01:38.200 --> 01:40.880
<font color="cyan">She's given me two girls.</font>
<font color="cyan">It's time for a boy.</font>

01:40.880 --> 01:43.040
<font color="white">What's the odds? </font><font color="cyan">Dead cert.</font>

01:43.040 --> 01:45.560
<font color="cyan">I'll give you 3-1 against.</font>

01:45.560 --> 01:47.760
<font color="white">Oh, I'll have a few bob on that!</font>
<font color="cyan">All right!</font>

01:48.840 --> 01:51.120
<font color="cyan">Gin. All boys!</font>

01:54.480 --> 01:56.760
<font color="white">FRED SIGHS</font>

01:57.800 --> 02:00.160
<font color="white">BABY CRIES</font>

02:00.160 --> 02:02.680
<font color="white">MAN: Could you excuse</font>
<font color="white">me one moment, please?</font>

02:06.800 --> 02:09.280
<font color="white">Timothy! What happened?</font>

02:09.280 --> 02:11.680
<font color="cyan">We were spinning around at playtime.</font>

02:11.680 --> 02:13.440
<font color="white">And school let you leave?</font>

02:13.440 --> 02:17.000
<font color="white">Somebody should have come with you.</font>
<font color="cyan">I told them I knew how to get here.</font>

02:17.000 --> 02:20.000
<font color="cyan">You're always at work.</font>
<font color="white">What if I was away on a call?</font>

02:20.000 --> 02:23.000
<font color="lime">Is everything all right, Doctor?</font>
<font color="white">They just sent him here!</font>

02:23.000 --> 02:25.040
<font color="white">Why can't they deal with that</font>
<font color="white">at school?</font>

02:25.040 --> 02:28.280
<font color="white">It's only a graze. </font><font color="lime">Let me see here...</font>

02:29.920 --> 02:32.440
<font color="lime">Well, I think we're definitely</font>
<font color="lime">going to need a bandage.</font>

02:32.440 --> 02:34.200
<font color="lime">We should clean it first, though.</font>

02:35.680 --> 02:37.680
<font color="white">Will you be all right</font>
<font color="white">with Sister Bernadette,</font>

02:37.680 --> 02:39.360
<font color="white">while I finish seeing to my patient?</font>

02:39.360 --> 02:41.200
<font color="white">You're very kind, Sister.</font>

02:41.200 --> 02:44.200
<font color="lime">Let's get you sat down and we'll</font>
<font color="lime">have that fixed up in a jiffy.</font>

02:47.200 --> 02:49.080
<font color="yellow">Afternoon, Jane.</font>

02:50.880 --> 02:53.160
<font color="white">BABIES CRY</font>

02:54.080 --> 02:56.000
<font color="white">Looking forward</font>
<font color="white">to tonight, Nurse Lee?</font>

02:56.000 --> 02:58.320
<font color="yellow">Oh, yes, it's yonks</font>
<font color="yellow">since I've been to a fair.</font>

02:58.320 --> 03:00.640
<font color="white">What about you, Jane.</font>
<font color="white">Are you excited?</font>

03:00.640 --> 03:01.840
<font color="lime">Yes.</font>

03:02.840 --> 03:04.320
<font color="white">We can tell.</font>

03:06.320 --> 03:07.920
<font color="white">They were filthy, the poor loves,</font>

03:07.920 --> 03:09.960
<font color="white">they looked like</font>
<font color="white">bleedin' chimney sweeps.</font>

03:11.960 --> 03:13.640
<font color="white">All right, Rubes?</font>

03:13.640 --> 03:15.840
<font color="cyan">Oh, hello, Joyce, how are you today?</font>

03:15.840 --> 03:18.200
<font color="white">I'm quite well. How are YOU today?</font>

03:19.160 --> 03:21.480
<font color="cyan">Ain't nothing wrong</font>
<font color="cyan">with trying to better oneself.</font>

03:21.480 --> 03:23.920
<font color="white">Ain't nothing wrong</font>
<font color="white">with being what you are, neither.</font>

03:23.920 --> 03:28.120
<font color="white">THEY GIGGLE</font>
<font color="cyan">Well, MY husband has</font>
<font color="cyan">been promoted to supervisor.</font>

03:28.120 --> 03:30.240
<font color="cyan">The youngest ever, they say.</font>

03:30.240 --> 03:32.360
<font color="white">You live on the same street as me!</font>

03:32.360 --> 03:34.840
<font color="white">Your roof leaks as badly as mine,</font>

03:34.840 --> 03:37.000
<font color="white">and your backside</font>
<font color="white">don't smell of roses, does it?!</font>

03:37.000 --> 03:39.120
<font color="white">THEY TITTER</font>

03:39.120 --> 03:42.040
<font color="cyan">Quite right. It smells of lavender.</font>

03:42.040 --> 03:44.720
<font color="cyan">And I'm very sorry</font>
<font color="cyan">to hear about your roof.</font>

03:44.720 --> 03:46.600
<font color="cyan">We can recommend a good man.</font>

03:50.360 --> 03:52.680
<font color="white">DOORBELL RINGS</font>

03:55.280 --> 03:57.760
<font color="lime">Good evening. </font><font color="white">It is, indeed.</font>

03:57.760 --> 03:59.760
<font color="white">And you must be...Sister Julienne?</font>

03:59.760 --> 04:02.040
<font color="lime">I am. And you are...?</font>

04:03.920 --> 04:06.000
<font color="white">The Reverend Applebee-Thornton.</font>

04:06.000 --> 04:09.200
<font color="lime">Indeed!</font>
<font color="lime">Erm, Nurse Noakes sent us a letter.</font>

04:09.200 --> 04:11.320
<font color="white">Oh, wonderful! Ha!</font>

04:11.320 --> 04:15.040
<font color="white">Wonderful! Ha... Now, er,</font>
<font color="white">I don't wish to be a burden on you,</font>

04:15.040 --> 04:17.519
<font color="white">I simply couldn't take advantage</font>
<font color="white">of your hospitality</font>

04:17.519 --> 04:19.079
<font color="white">without giving something back.</font>

04:19.079 --> 04:21.839
<font color="white">Now, I would like to offer</font>
<font color="white">chaplaincy to your patients.</font>

04:21.839 --> 04:24.880
<font color="lime">We're very happy to shelter you,</font>
<font color="lime">until your new parish...</font>

04:24.880 --> 04:27.440
<font color="white">Chummy spoke so fondly</font>
<font color="white">about everybody here.</font>

04:27.440 --> 04:30.360
<font color="white">What a wonderfully</font>
<font color="white">vibrant woman she is.</font>

04:30.360 --> 04:33.840
<font color="white">The tribes people were thoroughly</font>
<font color="white">fascinated on her arrival, you know.</font>

04:33.840 --> 04:36.160
<font color="white">I don't think they'd seen</font>
<font color="white">anything quite like her.</font>

04:36.160 --> 04:38.960
<font color="white">They refer to her as Boku-Uman,</font>

04:38.960 --> 04:42.240
<font color="white">which translates as "a lot of woman"!</font>

04:42.240 --> 04:44.920
<font color="white">Ha-ha-ha! One of the younger men</font>
<font color="white">challenged her to a wrestle -</font>

04:44.920 --> 04:47.520
<font color="white">that fine fellow Noakes,</font>
<font color="white">he stepped in - I don't think</font>

04:47.520 --> 04:49.640
<font color="white">she's quite recovered since!</font>
<font color="lime">Reverend...</font>

04:49.640 --> 04:53.240
<font color="white">Y... </font><font color="lime">A friend of Nurse Noakes</font>
<font color="lime">is a friend of Nonnatus House.</font>

04:53.240 --> 04:56.440
<font color="lime">I believe your parish lodgings</font>
<font color="lime">will not be ready for some time.</font>

04:56.440 --> 04:59.240
<font color="lime">You're welcome,</font>
<font color="lime">for as long as it takes. </font><font color="white">Oh...!</font>

04:59.240 --> 05:02.200
<font color="lime">Would you care for something to eat,</font>
<font color="lime">before I show you to your room?</font>

05:02.200 --> 05:05.720
<font color="white">Oh, very kind!</font>
<font color="white">I have been regaled with tales</font>

05:05.720 --> 05:08.400
<font color="white">of Mrs B's prowess in the kitchen!</font>

05:08.400 --> 05:12.480
<font color="cyan">I...I dare say that the language</font>
<font color="cyan">barrier will be less of a problem</font>

05:12.480 --> 05:15.840
<font color="cyan">with the Cockneys, although</font>
<font color="cyan">I believe this rhyming slang...</font>

05:19.160 --> 05:20.520
<font color="white">DOOR CREAKS</font>

05:23.000 --> 05:24.680
<font color="cyan">How drunk are you, then?</font>

05:25.720 --> 05:27.280
<font color="white">Oh...</font>

05:27.280 --> 05:29.600
<font color="white">Not as bad as Christmas.</font>

05:29.600 --> 05:31.360
<font color="cyan">You been gambling?</font>

05:31.360 --> 05:34.640
<font color="white">Gambling?! Ruby, my love,</font>
<font color="white">I'm a reformed character!</font>

05:34.640 --> 05:35.840
<font color="cyan">Yeah(!)</font>

05:36.800 --> 05:38.880
<font color="white">I'm saving up</font>
<font color="white">to get us out of this pit.</font>

05:38.880 --> 05:42.400
<font color="cyan">Then why can I hear the jangling</font>
<font color="cyan">of coins, whenever you move?</font>

05:46.120 --> 05:49.040
<font color="white">It ain't gambling</font>
<font color="white">if you know you're going to win.</font>

05:49.040 --> 05:50.560
<font color="white">Ha-ha!</font>

05:50.560 --> 05:52.680
<font color="cyan">You are a bad man.</font>

06:01.960 --> 06:03.640
<font color="white">How's my boy doing in there?</font>

06:03.640 --> 06:05.360
<font color="cyan">He's tip-top.</font>

06:05.360 --> 06:08.520
<font color="cyan">Not much of a mover,</font>
<font color="cyan">unlike the other two.</font>

06:08.520 --> 06:10.920
<font color="white">He's a cool dude,</font>
<font color="white">like that James Dean.</font>

06:11.920 --> 06:14.240
<font color="white">No need for carrying on,</font>
<font color="white">is there, boy?</font>

06:14.240 --> 06:15.840
<font color="white">(You take it easy in there.)</font>

06:17.320 --> 06:20.240
<font color="cyan">I was a lucky girl</font>
<font color="cyan">to land you, Dougie.</font>

06:24.640 --> 06:26.960
<font color="white">It was a movie kiss,</font>
<font color="white">through the wire fence,</font>

06:26.960 --> 06:30.280
<font color="white">then he went to his plane,</font>
<font color="white">a cheeky wink, and he was off!</font>

06:30.280 --> 06:31.960
<font color="white">THEY LAUGH</font>
<font color="white">Jenny's turn!</font>

06:33.000 --> 06:35.000
<font color="yellow">We were playing sardines,</font>

06:35.000 --> 06:38.120
<font color="yellow">there were six of us</font>
<font color="yellow">squashed into a wardrobe,</font>

06:38.120 --> 06:41.960
<font color="yellow">someone kissed me and, to this day,</font>
<font color="yellow">I don't know who it was!</font>

06:41.960 --> 06:45.720
<font color="white">Well, I do hope I'm not</font>
<font color="white">entirely surrounded by harlots!</font>

06:45.720 --> 06:48.520
<font color="white">Cynthia?</font>
<font color="cyan">Well, I knew his name, at least,</font>

06:48.520 --> 06:51.080
<font color="cyan">but it was nothing like</font>
<font color="cyan">a movie kiss.</font>

06:51.080 --> 06:52.960
<font color="cyan">I was eight. </font><font color="yellow">Cynthia!</font>

06:52.960 --> 06:55.240
<font color="white">I will never look at you</font>
<font color="white">with the same eyes again!</font>

06:55.240 --> 06:57.880
<font color="cyan">Don't be silly! </font><font color="white">Oh, dear Jane,</font>

06:57.880 --> 07:01.200
<font color="white">you must think us silly girls,</font>
<font color="white">to be excited about first kisses.</font>

07:01.200 --> 07:05.920
<font color="lime">Not at all. </font><font color="white">I know, let's name</font>
<font color="white">the goldfish after your first kiss.</font>

07:05.920 --> 07:08.480
<font color="cyan">That's a wonderful idea!</font>
<font color="yellow">Yes, spill the beans, Jane -</font>

07:08.480 --> 07:10.280
<font color="yellow">what's our goldfish called?</font>

07:10.280 --> 07:13.840
<font color="lime">No, I... </font><font color="white">It doesn't matter how</font>
<font color="white">silly the name is, we'll go with it.</font>

07:17.400 --> 07:20.120
<font color="lime">Well, I'm afraid this goldfish</font>
<font color="lime">shall be nameless, then.</font>

07:35.080 --> 07:37.120
<font color="white">CUTLERY CLINKS ON CROCKERY</font>

07:54.960 --> 07:57.640
<font color="cyan">Do you think</font>
<font color="cyan">she's all right, Sister?</font>

07:57.640 --> 08:01.880
<font color="lime">Jane is a quiet soul,</font>
<font color="lime">not one for displaying her emotions.</font>

08:01.880 --> 08:03.080
<font color="lime">It's hard to tell.</font>

08:03.080 --> 08:06.160
<font color="white">But to have lived her life</font>
<font color="white">without so much as a kiss.</font>

08:06.160 --> 08:09.120
<font color="lime">You are speaking to a nun, Trixie.</font>

08:09.120 --> 08:11.280
<font color="white">Oh, yes, sorry.</font>

08:11.280 --> 08:15.280
<font color="lime">I sympathise, I really do, but as</font>
<font color="lime">Jane is practically silent around</font>

08:15.280 --> 08:18.960
<font color="lime">her colleagues, the ability to speak</font>
<font color="lime">to men is probably beyond her.</font>

08:20.760 --> 08:22.800
<font color="white">Where did Sister Julienne find her?</font>

08:22.800 --> 08:24.320
<font color="lime">That wouldn't be for me to say.</font>

08:24.320 --> 08:30.480
<font color="white">Good morning, all!</font>
<font color="white">Ah, we have a fuller compliment.</font>

08:30.480 --> 08:32.200
<font color="white">Kushe-o!</font>

08:32.200 --> 08:33.600
<font color="white">Which means "hello".</font>

08:50.080 --> 08:53.960
<font color="white">And it is my belief</font>
<font color="white">that Nurse Noakes' calling came from</font>

08:53.960 --> 08:58.680
<font color="white">her humanity, as much as it did</font>
<font color="white">the Lord God Almighty.</font>

08:58.680 --> 09:03.560
<font color="white">Now, the humanity</font>
<font color="white">in this lovely bread!</font>

09:03.560 --> 09:05.840
<font color="white">Oh, we had nothing</font>
<font color="white">this fine in Sierra Leone,</font>

09:05.840 --> 09:11.400
<font color="white">although they do have Cassava Leaf</font>
<font color="white">Plassas, which is Chummy's favourite.</font>

09:11.400 --> 09:12.760
<font color="white">I'll tell you how we make them...</font>

09:12.760 --> 09:14.240
<font color="white">KNOCKING</font>

09:14.240 --> 09:15.720
<font color="yellow">I'll get it.</font>

09:21.360 --> 09:23.640
<font color="white">LOUD KNOCKING CONTINUES</font>

09:23.640 --> 09:25.280
<font color="cyan">She's about to pop.</font>

09:25.280 --> 09:28.480
<font color="cyan">Screaming the house down. Told me</font>
<font color="cyan">to bring a midwife, straight away.</font>

09:28.480 --> 09:31.200
<font color="cyan">Phone's buggere-...er, broken.</font>
<font color="yellow">I'll fetch my things.</font>

09:31.200 --> 09:33.160
<font color="lime">Not so fast. Hello, Douglas.</font>

09:33.160 --> 09:36.360
<font color="cyan">Sister. </font><font color="lime">I did both of Ruby's girls</font>
<font color="lime">and they were beauties.</font>

09:36.360 --> 09:39.680
<font color="yellow">But I'm first on call, Sister.</font>
<font color="lime">Then you can assist.</font>

09:39.680 --> 09:42.160
<font color="cyan">She said to "try and get</font>
<font color="cyan">Sister Evangelina, if you can.</font>

09:42.160 --> 09:43.680
<font color="cyan">"She delivers 'em best."</font>

09:48.000 --> 09:49.480
<font color="yellow">Mrs Roberts, Sister. </font><font color="cyan">God speed.</font>

09:51.840 --> 09:57.320
<font color="lime">So, Sister Julienne, which of your</font>
<font color="lime">charges shall I accompany, hm?</font>

09:57.320 --> 10:00.040
<font color="lime">I promise they will receive</font>
<font color="lime">exclusive stories in recompense.</font>

10:04.360 --> 10:07.480
<font color="white">You should accompany me</font>
<font color="white">on your first day, Reverend.</font>

10:07.480 --> 10:09.360
<font color="white">Start at the bottom</font>
<font color="white">and work your way up.</font>

10:21.280 --> 10:22.400
<font color="cyan">They're 'ere.</font>

10:24.440 --> 10:26.320
<font color="cyan">I'll put some more hot water on.</font>

10:26.320 --> 10:29.040
<font color="lime">Good lad. Hello there, Ruby.</font>

10:29.040 --> 10:30.960
<font color="lime">Here we are again!</font>

10:30.960 --> 10:34.720
<font color="white">Sister, I feel terrible.</font>
<font color="white">Look at the state of me.</font>

10:34.720 --> 10:38.000
<font color="lime">It's not a beauty contest,</font>
<font color="lime">come on. How are you doing?</font>

10:38.000 --> 10:40.560
<font color="lime">This is Nurse Lee.</font>
<font color="yellow">Hello, Mrs Roberts.</font>

10:40.560 --> 10:43.800
<font color="white">This one hurts like hell.</font>
<font color="white">No offence.</font>

10:43.800 --> 10:48.520
<font color="lime">No, none taken. There you go,</font>
<font color="lime">on the edge, that's it.</font>

10:48.520 --> 10:51.280
<font color="lime">They say you forget with time</font>
<font color="lime">how much it did hurt.</font>

10:52.400 --> 10:55.840
<font color="white">Ooh! </font><font color="lime">All right. There you are.</font>

11:00.000 --> 11:01.480
<font color="lime">That's it! There you go.</font>

11:05.880 --> 11:07.400
<font color="white">He's early, isn't he?</font>

11:07.400 --> 11:09.280
<font color="lime">When was the last pain?</font>

11:09.280 --> 11:10.480
<font color="white">Just before you got here.</font>

11:19.120 --> 11:20.320
<font color="lime">Heartbeat's strong.</font>

11:21.400 --> 11:22.920
<font color="white">I feel scared, Sister.</font>

11:24.520 --> 11:26.200
<font color="lime">All be over soon.</font>

11:26.200 --> 11:27.760
<font color="lime">My old matron used to say</font>

11:27.760 --> 11:30.400
<font color="lime">"You've had your sweets,</font>
<font color="lime">now take your sours."</font>

11:32.880 --> 11:36.960
<font color="lime">All right. We'll turn her on</font>
<font color="lime">her side, have a look after this.</font>

11:42.320 --> 11:45.560
<font color="lime">All right keep breathing,</font>
<font color="lime">keep breathing. That's a girl.</font>

11:45.560 --> 11:47.440
<font color="yellow">It's all right, Ruby. </font><font color="lime">Good girl.</font>

11:59.000 --> 12:00.560
<font color="lime">That's it.</font>

12:08.320 --> 12:09.760
<font color="white">I told you it hurt more.</font>

12:09.760 --> 12:13.840
<font color="lime">No one's doubting that now.</font>
<font color="lime">Baby's crowning, looks a big one.</font>

12:13.840 --> 12:15.640
<font color="white">They said I was on the small side.</font>

12:15.640 --> 12:17.920
<font color="lime">They can't see what I can.</font>

12:17.920 --> 12:21.480
<font color="yellow">Nearly there, Ruby. If Sister</font>
<font color="yellow">can see baby, we're not far away.</font>

12:21.480 --> 12:23.600
<font color="white">It hurts! </font><font color="yellow">Not long now.</font>

12:26.800 --> 12:28.520
<font color="white">It'll be as beautiful</font>
<font color="white">as its sisters.</font>

12:28.520 --> 12:33.280
<font color="lime">Now, on the next one, I want you</font>
<font color="lime">to give us a really big push, Ruby.</font>

12:33.280 --> 12:36.400
<font color="white">I'll buy him a blue bonnet.</font>
<font color="yellow">Baby blue?</font>

12:36.400 --> 12:39.480
<font color="white">Yeah, yeah,</font>
<font color="white">with little duckies on it. </font><font color="yellow">Lovely.</font>

12:41.840 --> 12:44.680
<font color="yellow">Good girl, keep going!</font>
<font color="yellow">Keep going, good girl!</font>

12:44.680 --> 12:48.320
<font color="yellow">Really big push. Good girl.</font>
<font color="yellow">Keep going, that's really good.</font>

12:48.320 --> 12:49.680
<font color="yellow">Good girl! </font><font color="lime">Yes, come on.</font>

12:49.680 --> 12:52.960
<font color="yellow">The head's nearly out,</font>
<font color="yellow">we're nearly there now!</font>

12:52.960 --> 12:55.200
<font color="lime">Wait. </font><font color="yellow">Stop pushing. Short breaths.</font>

12:56.760 --> 13:00.560
<font color="yellow">When the next contraction comes,</font>
<font color="yellow">I want you to push hard, all right?</font>

13:04.800 --> 13:06.600
<font color="yellow">Good girl! That's it.</font>

13:06.600 --> 13:11.920
<font color="yellow">Really big push, Ruby.</font>
<font color="yellow">He's here! He's...</font>

13:16.680 --> 13:18.720
<font color="white">SILENCE</font>

13:30.600 --> 13:34.200
<font color="lime">Towel? Nurse!</font>
<font color="white">SHE SIGHS</font>

13:38.360 --> 13:40.360
<font color="lime">See to mother, Nurse Lee.</font>

13:54.560 --> 13:59.280
<font color="white">BABY CRIES</font>
<font color="white">Thank God. Oh, thank God for that.</font>

14:08.960 --> 14:11.000
<font color="yellow">Sister?</font>

14:11.000 --> 14:13.560
<font color="lime">Let's have some gauze</font>
<font color="lime">soaked in boiled water.</font>

14:16.640 --> 14:18.960
<font color="lime">Nurse Lee, damp gauze.</font>

14:24.800 --> 14:25.840
<font color="white">It's a boy?</font>

14:31.040 --> 14:33.600
<font color="cyan">Hey, hey! Daddy's here!</font>

14:33.600 --> 14:35.240
<font color="white">It's a boy, Douglas.</font>

14:35.240 --> 14:38.040
<font color="cyan">Course he is. I never doubted it.</font>
<font color="yellow">We haven't quite finished yet.</font>

14:38.040 --> 14:40.600
<font color="cyan">I brought us a drink.</font>
<font color="lime">No-one in here yet please, Douglas.</font>

14:40.600 --> 14:42.120
<font color="white">Oh, he's all right, I want him here.</font>

14:42.120 --> 14:45.000
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, I must insist. The</font>
<font color="yellow">afterbirth hasn't been delivered.</font>

14:45.000 --> 14:46.480
<font color="cyan">The what? </font><font color="yellow">Please, Mr Roberts.</font>

14:48.920 --> 14:52.280
<font color="white">He's seen worse,</font>
<font color="white">after ten years of marriage!</font>

14:53.560 --> 14:55.920
<font color="yellow">Let's get you neat and tidy first.</font>

14:55.920 --> 14:58.480
<font color="white">BABY GURGLES</font>

14:58.480 --> 14:59.960
<font color="white">I love that sound.</font>

15:19.800 --> 15:22.480
<font color="yellow">Placenta successfully delivered,</font>
<font color="yellow">Sister.</font>

15:22.480 --> 15:24.320
<font color="lime">That's good.</font>

15:24.320 --> 15:26.080
<font color="white">All done?</font>

15:26.080 --> 15:27.320
<font color="yellow">Yes, all done.</font>

15:32.760 --> 15:34.760
<font color="yellow">Can I get you</font>
<font color="yellow">a glass of water, Ruby?</font>

15:36.000 --> 15:37.440
<font color="white">What's wrong?</font>

15:38.680 --> 15:40.360
<font color="white">What's wrong!</font>

15:41.440 --> 15:44.560
<font color="lime">Nurse Lee, would you ring</font>
<font color="lime">for the doctor now, please?</font>

15:47.720 --> 15:51.960
<font color="white">What's wrong? Sister Evangelina,</font>
<font color="white">what's wrong with him?</font>

15:51.960 --> 15:55.720
<font color="white">You tell me what's going on</font>
<font color="white">right now! What is it?</font>

15:57.320 --> 16:04.280
<font color="lime">Baby's had some complications, Ruby.</font>
<font color="lime">There's a problem with his back.</font>

16:06.720 --> 16:09.680
<font color="white">And so I wrapped</font>
<font color="white">all the fruit in brown paper</font>

16:09.680 --> 16:11.760
<font color="white">and used goat's wool as a beard.</font>

16:11.760 --> 16:15.080
<font color="white">And hey, presto,</font>
<font color="white">Christmas in Sierra Leone.</font>

16:15.080 --> 16:18.800
<font color="white">Of course, the nativity is no real</font>
<font color="white">surprise to the tribespeople.</font>

16:18.800 --> 16:21.600
<font color="white">A child born in a stable</font>
<font color="white">seemed perfectly reasonable.</font>
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS.</font>

16:21.600 --> 16:23.840
<font color="cyan">I should... </font><font color="white">Oh, yes, absolutely.</font>

16:36.680 --> 16:38.920
<font color="white">I don't believe</font>
<font color="white">I've had the pleasure?</font>

16:40.560 --> 16:43.520
<font color="white">The Reverend Applebee-Thornton.</font>

16:43.520 --> 16:46.840
<font color="lime">Jane. </font><font color="white">Yes.</font>
<font color="white">I'm sorry if I startled you.</font>

16:46.840 --> 16:49.480
<font color="white">Oh, my dear.</font>
<font color="white">Oh no, your fish isn't that hungry.</font>

16:49.480 --> 16:53.760
<font color="white">No, we must rescue the poor fellow,</font>
<font color="white">before he eats himself to death,</font>

16:53.760 --> 16:54.880
<font color="white">like a Roman Emperor.</font>

16:56.960 --> 16:59.440
<font color="white">Oh, no, no, the scales</font>
<font color="white">are too delicate to touch.</font>

16:59.440 --> 17:01.360
<font color="white">We must scoop him out gently.</font>

17:07.640 --> 17:12.240
<font color="white">Absolutely ideal.</font>
<font color="white">Time is of the essence.</font>

17:16.000 --> 17:17.000
<font color="white">Yes, thank you.</font>

17:27.359 --> 17:29.920
<font color="white">And now we need to change</font>
<font color="white">the water in the bowl.</font>

17:46.400 --> 17:48.440
<font color="white">Now, let's put</font>
<font color="white">a tad more warm in there.</font>

17:48.440 --> 17:52.240
<font color="white">Needs to be room temperature, so</font>
<font color="white">the little one doesn't die of shock.</font>

17:56.160 --> 17:58.880
<font color="white">In Sierra Leone, you know,</font>
<font color="white">they had sharks in the river.</font>

17:58.880 --> 18:02.920
<font color="white">Huge beasts, apparently.</font>
<font color="white">I was unfortunate never to see one.</font>

18:04.560 --> 18:07.520
<font color="white">Right. Perfect!</font>

18:11.840 --> 18:13.600
<font color="cyan">Apologies, ready when you are.</font>

18:34.760 --> 18:36.960
<font color="white">It's hydrocephalus -</font>

18:36.960 --> 18:40.200
<font color="white">water on the brain caused by</font>
<font color="white">the break in the spinal cord.</font>

18:41.240 --> 18:44.280
<font color="white">That's what spina bifida means.</font>
<font color="white">It's Latin for...</font>

18:49.200 --> 18:52.240
<font color="white">We're taking him</font>
<font color="white">to the London Hospital.</font>

18:52.240 --> 18:54.720
<font color="white">The medical advancements</font>
<font color="white">in treating this condition</font>

18:54.720 --> 18:57.120
<font color="white">have come on leaps and bounds</font>
<font color="white">over the past few years.</font>

18:57.120 --> 18:59.720
<font color="white">The surgeons are second to none.</font>

18:59.720 --> 19:03.440
<font color="white">Your son will receive the best</font>
<font color="white">treatment in the world, Mr Roberts.</font>

19:05.200 --> 19:08.520
<font color="white">See to your ladies.</font>
<font color="white">We'll take great care of your son.</font>

20:32.720 --> 20:36.440
<font color="yellow">Mr Roberts?</font>
<font color="yellow">One of the girls let me in.</font>

20:41.960 --> 20:44.200
<font color="yellow">I'm told baby's doing well.</font>

20:44.200 --> 20:47.120
<font color="yellow">He should be ready to come home</font>
<font color="yellow">from the hospital tomorrow.</font>

20:51.160 --> 20:52.400
<font color="yellow">How is Mrs Roberts?</font>

20:54.600 --> 20:55.600
<font color="cyan">See for yourself.</font>

21:04.520 --> 21:05.680
<font color="yellow">Mrs Roberts?</font>

21:05.680 --> 21:08.120
<font color="white">Nurse Lee. You caught me red-handed.</font>

21:09.200 --> 21:12.080
<font color="yellow">You're out of bed.</font>

21:12.080 --> 21:16.200
<font color="white">Doesn't do no harm to look good, does</font>
<font color="white">it? Lifts the spirits, so they say.</font>

21:17.520 --> 21:19.440
<font color="yellow">I suppose.</font>

21:19.440 --> 21:21.800
<font color="white">Can't wallow forever. Things to do.</font>

21:25.000 --> 21:26.760
<font color="yellow">I was just telling your husband,</font>

21:26.760 --> 21:30.560
<font color="yellow">baby's doing well. He should be</font>
<font color="yellow">back... </font><font color="white">Oh, that's excellent.</font>

21:30.560 --> 21:33.000
<font color="white">Wonderful news.</font>
<font color="white">We'll soon have him back, then?</font>

21:33.000 --> 21:35.200
<font color="white">That's wonderful.</font>

21:41.760 --> 21:43.280
<font color="yellow">'She took it badly at first,'</font>

21:43.280 --> 21:45.840
<font color="yellow">but now she seems</font>
<font color="yellow">in very good spirits.</font>

21:45.840 --> 21:49.280
<font color="white">I remember my first</font>
<font color="white">spina bifida birth.</font>

21:49.280 --> 21:54.800
<font color="white">It looked like a huge dollop</font>
<font color="white">of raspberry jam on baby's back.</font>

21:57.240 --> 22:00.400
<font color="white">Of course, back then,</font>
<font color="white">the humane course for treatment</font>

22:00.400 --> 22:02.680
<font color="white">was considered</font>
<font color="white">to be chloral hydrate.</font>

22:03.960 --> 22:06.760
<font color="white">Let the child pass peacefully.</font>

22:06.760 --> 22:09.400
<font color="yellow">No! </font><font color="cyan">That was when there</font>
<font color="cyan">was little that could be done</font>

22:09.400 --> 22:11.920
<font color="cyan">and it was considered a kindness.</font>

22:11.920 --> 22:13.600
<font color="cyan">There is much more to be done now.</font>

22:13.600 --> 22:18.120
<font color="lime">But the child will, more often</font>
<font color="lime">than not, have no bowel control,</font>

22:18.120 --> 22:21.440
<font color="lime">will have renal complications</font>
<font color="lime">and a drastically reduced lifespan,</font>

22:21.440 --> 22:24.480
<font color="lime">and for the rest of that short life,</font>
<font color="lime">it will be confined to a wheelchair.</font>

22:24.480 --> 22:26.320
<font color="cyan">Life is never without hope, Sister.</font>

22:26.320 --> 22:28.400
<font color="yellow">I know it won't be easy</font>
<font color="yellow">for the parents,</font>

22:28.400 --> 22:30.560
<font color="yellow">but I'm sure</font>
<font color="yellow">they're capable of coping.</font>

22:30.560 --> 22:32.720
<font color="white">The mothers don't listen, do they?</font>

22:32.720 --> 22:37.040
<font color="white">They're told again and again</font>
<font color="white">to avoid green potatoes.</font>

22:37.040 --> 22:39.880
<font color="lime">Green potatoes</font>
<font color="lime">no more cause spina bifida</font>

22:39.880 --> 22:42.360
<font color="lime">as the moon is made of cheese,</font>
<font color="lime">Sister Monica Joan.</font>

22:42.360 --> 22:45.440
<font color="cyan">I read recently</font>
<font color="cyan">it is considered now to be a myth,</font>

22:45.440 --> 22:49.080
<font color="cyan">although the actual cause</font>
<font color="cyan">is still unknown.</font>

22:49.080 --> 22:52.000
<font color="white">Therefore,</font>
<font color="white">the moon may yet be edible.</font>

22:53.240 --> 22:57.440
<font color="lime">Good evening, one and all.</font>
<font color="lime">What a remarkable constitutional.</font>

22:57.440 --> 22:59.800
<font color="lime">A balmy evening by the docks...</font>

22:59.800 --> 23:01.800
<font color="cyan">Reverend?</font>

23:01.800 --> 23:03.680
<font color="lime">Oh, thank you, Sister.</font>

23:03.680 --> 23:06.800
<font color="cyan">I have important administration</font>
<font color="cyan">to take care of tomorrow,</font>

23:06.800 --> 23:10.360
<font color="cyan">so would you be happy</font>
<font color="cyan">to accompany one of our nurses?</font>

23:10.360 --> 23:13.120
<font color="cyan">I'm sure any of them would be</font>
<font color="cyan">pleased to have your assistance.</font>

23:13.120 --> 23:17.800
<font color="white">Well, I've thoroughly enjoyed</font>
<font color="white">working with all your charges,</font>

23:17.800 --> 23:20.240
<font color="white">Sister,</font>
<font color="white">I couldn't possibly decide...</font>

23:20.240 --> 23:21.400
<font color="lime">Jane.</font>

23:23.600 --> 23:27.600
<font color="lime">I mean, I believe Jane</font>
<font color="lime">has rounds in the morning,</font>

23:27.600 --> 23:30.600
<font color="lime">and would benefit</font>
<font color="lime">from an extra pair of hands.</font>

23:30.600 --> 23:32.680
<font color="cyan">Jane?</font>

23:35.680 --> 23:39.000
<font color="lime">That would be delightful,</font>
<font color="lime">I look forward to it.</font>

23:39.000 --> 23:40.840
<font color="white">Shall we eat?</font>

23:45.160 --> 23:48.440
<font color="white">Are the carrots yours, as well?</font>
<font color="lime">Yes, the carrots are...</font>

23:48.440 --> 23:50.840
<font color="white">DOOR CREAKS</font>

23:50.840 --> 23:52.560
<font color="cyan">Here he is, girls.</font>

24:15.840 --> 24:17.640
<font color="cyan">Say hello to your brother, then.</font>

24:27.960 --> 24:30.200
<font color="cyan">We have to change</font>
<font color="cyan">the dressings every two days</font>

24:30.200 --> 24:32.040
<font color="cyan">and keep using this antiseptic.</font>

24:36.440 --> 24:38.000
<font color="lime">What's wrong with his legs?</font>

24:42.600 --> 24:45.920
<font color="cyan">Right, come on, little monsters.</font>
<font color="cyan">We'll come back up soon.</font>

25:03.400 --> 25:06.480
<font color="white">BABY CRIES</font>

25:22.160 --> 25:24.680
<font color="white">FLIES BUZZ</font>

25:33.800 --> 25:37.280
<font color="white">Should I perhaps tidy round a little?</font>
<font color="white">Would that be useful? </font><font color="lime">No.</font>

25:39.320 --> 25:41.840
<font color="lime">Does my house offend you, Vicar?</font>

25:41.840 --> 25:43.440
<font color="white">Oh, it's Reverend, actually.</font>

25:43.440 --> 25:47.800
<font color="white">No, it does not.</font>
<font color="lime">Well, it bloody well does, me.</font>

25:47.800 --> 25:49.120
<font color="white">Ow!</font>

25:49.120 --> 25:51.440
<font color="lime">You hear that?</font>
<font color="lime">I said it bloody well does, me.</font>

25:51.440 --> 25:52.680
<font color="white">I've been bitten!</font>

25:52.680 --> 25:55.320
<font color="cyan">Be a sweetheart</font>
<font color="cyan">and shove him out the window.</font>

25:58.520 --> 26:02.520
<font color="white">May I say, I have spent</font>
<font color="white">the last year in Africa,</font>

26:02.520 --> 26:06.680
<font color="white">in a society that did not</font>
<font color="white">produce William Shakespeare.</font>

26:06.680 --> 26:11.040
<font color="white">Nor did it produce Sir Isaac Newton,</font>
<font color="white">Isambard Kingdom Brunel...</font>

26:11.040 --> 26:12.920
<font color="lime">I hope there's a point to this.</font>

26:12.920 --> 26:16.440
<font color="white">Well, we consider ourselves</font>
<font color="white">a civilised culture,</font>

26:16.440 --> 26:20.080
<font color="white">and yet we allow our elderly</font>
<font color="white">to live in...</font>

26:20.080 --> 26:22.440
<font color="white">I'm sorry, I really</font>
<font color="white">don't wish to make judgements...</font>

26:22.440 --> 26:26.000
<font color="lime">A flea pit? Surrounded by prossies?</font>
<font color="lime">Not fit for a dog?</font>

26:26.000 --> 26:29.680
<font color="white">Well, yes, and it saddens me greatly,</font>

26:29.680 --> 26:32.600
<font color="white">both as a Christian and as a human.</font>

26:32.600 --> 26:36.040
<font color="cyan">At our age,</font>
<font color="cyan">we're grateful for the days.</font>

26:36.040 --> 26:38.480
<font color="lime">Exactly, sweetheart.</font>

26:38.480 --> 26:43.040
<font color="lime">I'll take what pleasure I can,</font>
<font color="lime">whenever I can get it,</font>

26:43.040 --> 26:45.520
<font color="lime">because we're a long time dead, sir.</font>

26:53.080 --> 26:54.760
<font color="white">The tribespeople of Sierra Leone,</font>

26:54.760 --> 26:57.680
<font color="white">they treat their elderly</font>
<font color="white">with the utmost respect,</font>

26:57.680 --> 27:01.080
<font color="white">their wisdom unquestionable,</font>
<font color="white">having had the benefit of experience.</font>

27:03.440 --> 27:05.160
<font color="white">Oh, thank you. Thank you, Jane.</font>

27:05.160 --> 27:08.320
<font color="white">A remarkable resilience</font>
<font color="white">about the Giddings, though.</font>

27:08.320 --> 27:12.760
<font color="white">Their love - triumphant still,</font>
<font color="white">despite the circumstances.</font>

27:12.760 --> 27:14.560
<font color="white">It swells the heart, does it not?</font>

27:14.560 --> 27:16.760
<font color="cyan">'Ere, love's young dream. Hmph!</font>

27:27.560 --> 27:29.280
<font color="yellow">Oh, he looks really well.</font>

27:40.120 --> 27:42.240
<font color="yellow">I think he may need feeding.</font>

27:42.240 --> 27:43.840
<font color="white">No.</font>

27:45.800 --> 27:47.440
<font color="yellow">He's hungry, Mrs Roberts.</font>

27:47.440 --> 27:48.840
<font color="white">I ain't got none, it dried up!</font>

27:49.880 --> 27:51.600
<font color="white">He has powdered.</font>

27:51.600 --> 27:52.800
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

27:55.080 --> 27:57.840
<font color="yellow">I'll make up a bottle.</font>
<font color="yellow">Will you hold him?</font>

28:00.680 --> 28:04.560
<font color="yellow">Ruby...</font>
<font color="white">Douglas told me to stop working,</font>

28:04.560 --> 28:07.800
<font color="white">but I carried on,</font>
<font color="white">lifting them baskets.</font>

28:07.800 --> 28:10.440
<font color="white">I used to rest them on my bump</font>
<font color="white">when I was loading up.</font>

28:10.440 --> 28:12.800
<font color="white">What if that hurt his back?</font>

28:12.800 --> 28:14.640
<font color="yellow">Lots of women work.</font>

28:15.800 --> 28:17.280
<font color="yellow">You can't blame yourself.</font>

28:17.280 --> 28:18.640
<font color="white">Why can't I?</font>

28:19.680 --> 28:21.240
<font color="white">He came out of me like that.</font>

28:24.040 --> 28:25.320
<font color="white">Or was it God?</font>

28:26.400 --> 28:28.440
<font color="white">He punishes people, don't he?</font>

28:28.440 --> 28:31.080
<font color="white">Vanity is one</font>
<font color="white">of the deadly sins, they say.</font>

28:33.160 --> 28:37.280
<font color="white">Maybe it was Dougie's gambling.</font>
<font color="white">Didn't Jesus hate all that?</font>

28:39.440 --> 28:40.640
<font color="white">We did something.</font>

28:42.440 --> 28:44.520
<font color="white">One of them things</font>
<font color="white">made him like that.</font>

28:47.960 --> 28:49.400
<font color="white">What did we do?!</font>

28:58.760 --> 29:00.120
<font color="yellow">I'll feed him.</font>

29:33.440 --> 29:35.760
<font color="yellow">Do you have the powdered milk,</font>
<font color="yellow">Mr Roberts?</font>

29:44.720 --> 29:45.920
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

29:49.640 --> 29:52.840
<font color="yellow">Do you think you could maybe take</font>
<font color="yellow">baby for a walk after he's fed?</font>

29:54.200 --> 29:56.640
<font color="yellow">Perhaps you could take the girls?</font>

29:56.640 --> 29:58.920
<font color="yellow">He needs sunlight,</font>
<font color="yellow">and it's a lovely day.</font>

29:58.920 --> 30:01.320
<font color="cyan">A man doesn't go about</font>
<font color="cyan">pushing prams.</font>

30:02.920 --> 30:04.320
<font color="yellow">Perhaps the girls could?</font>

30:04.320 --> 30:05.640
<font color="cyan">No.</font>

30:05.640 --> 30:07.600
<font color="cyan">They're too young for this.</font>

30:07.600 --> 30:10.520
<font color="cyan">Neither of our mums are around</font>
<font color="cyan">anymore. They'd have helped us.</font>

30:10.520 --> 30:12.120
<font color="yellow">Of course.</font>

30:15.600 --> 30:19.040
<font color="yellow">Would you hold him,</font>
<font color="yellow">while I make up a bottle?</font>

30:38.240 --> 30:40.040
<font color="cyan">She even touched him yet?</font>

30:44.880 --> 30:47.880
<font color="yellow">Your wife is a little</font>
<font color="yellow">under the weather at the moment.</font>

31:02.080 --> 31:04.000
<font color="white">No point then, is there?</font>

31:07.840 --> 31:09.520
<font color="white">DOOR SLAMS</font>

31:13.440 --> 31:15.360
<font color="cyan">How are the Roberts, Nurse Lee?</font>

31:17.000 --> 31:20.440
<font color="yellow">I think father</font>
<font color="yellow">is capable of seeing it through...</font>

31:22.000 --> 31:24.240
<font color="yellow">..but mother</font>
<font color="yellow">has taken it very badly.</font>

31:24.240 --> 31:26.240
<font color="cyan">I do sympathise with her.</font>

31:26.240 --> 31:28.880
<font color="cyan">She has dreamt</font>
<font color="cyan">of a perfect, healthy child</font>

31:28.880 --> 31:30.480
<font color="cyan">since the day she conceived.</font>

31:39.800 --> 31:42.800
<font color="yellow">I knew, one day, I would</font>
<font color="yellow">encounter something like this...</font>

31:46.160 --> 31:48.480
<font color="yellow">..but I feel</font>
<font color="yellow">so under-prepared, Sister.</font>

31:49.560 --> 31:53.240
<font color="cyan">In what way?</font>
<font color="yellow">I don't know what to say to her.</font>

31:53.240 --> 31:56.480
<font color="yellow">How to help. I don't even know</font>
<font color="yellow">what options are available.</font>

32:03.640 --> 32:06.080
<font color="cyan">Serendipity is a wonderful thing.</font>

32:08.120 --> 32:10.880
<font color="cyan">You must accompany Jane</font>
<font color="cyan">to St Gideon's.</font>

32:10.880 --> 32:14.800
<font color="white">Once again, we are much indebted</font>
<font color="white">to the Sisters of Nonnatus House.</font>

32:14.800 --> 32:17.600
<font color="white">The generosity they elicit</font>
<font color="white">is astounding.</font>

32:19.800 --> 32:21.960
<font color="yellow">Could I ask, Mrs Peacock...</font>

32:23.960 --> 32:26.240
<font color="yellow">..how many of your patients,</font>
<font color="yellow">have families?</font>

32:26.240 --> 32:28.000
<font color="white">All of them, technically.</font>

32:28.000 --> 32:31.400
<font color="white">We have a number who were abandoned,</font>
<font color="white">although that's reducing,</font>

32:31.400 --> 32:33.280
<font color="white">thanks mainly to you midwives -</font>

32:33.280 --> 32:36.560
<font color="white">not so easy to abandon a child when</font>
<font color="white">a nurse is coming round to visit.</font>

32:36.560 --> 32:38.400
<font color="yellow">How could they, though?</font>

32:38.400 --> 32:40.960
<font color="white">Oh, often the mother feels guilty -</font>

32:40.960 --> 32:43.680
<font color="white">was it something she did?</font>
<font color="white">Was it her fault?</font>

32:47.400 --> 32:50.280
<font color="lime">Can you stay for a cup of tea?</font>

32:53.160 --> 32:55.040
<font color="yellow">I'm terribly sorry... </font><font color="white">Cup of tea.</font>

32:56.320 --> 33:00.320
<font color="yellow">Oh. No, thank you,</font>
<font color="yellow">we must be leaving soon.</font>

33:01.520 --> 33:03.320
<font color="lime">Hello, Jane.</font>

33:03.320 --> 33:06.680
<font color="lime">You're looking very well.</font>

33:06.680 --> 33:07.960
<font color="cyan">Hello, Jacob.</font>

33:07.960 --> 33:11.360
<font color="white">Away with you, Jacob! I thought</font>
<font color="white">I was the only girl for you?</font>

33:14.000 --> 33:15.920
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, I couldn't understand.</font>

33:15.920 --> 33:19.000
<font color="white">Oh, it comes with time,</font>
<font color="white">but don't let it fool you.</font>

33:19.000 --> 33:22.080
<font color="white">he's as bright as a button</font>
<font color="white">and as cheeky as a monkey.</font>

33:23.680 --> 33:25.680
<font color="yellow">I have a family, at the moment.</font>

33:26.880 --> 33:28.920
<font color="yellow">I imagine their child</font>
<font color="yellow">would do well here.</font>

33:30.280 --> 33:32.520
<font color="white">Let me make it very clear, Nurse,</font>

33:32.520 --> 33:34.600
<font color="white">this is a home by name only.</font>

33:35.880 --> 33:37.200
<font color="white">It is not "home".</font>

33:38.640 --> 33:40.720
<font color="white">If the child</font>
<font color="white">can stay with its family,</font>

33:40.720 --> 33:44.120
<font color="white">I suggest you do everything</font>
<font color="white">in your power to make that happen.</font>

33:47.520 --> 33:48.960
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

33:50.200 --> 33:52.040
<font color="white">It's lovely to see you again, Jane.</font>

33:53.440 --> 33:55.000
<font color="white">Still a chatterbox, then?</font>

34:02.960 --> 34:05.120
<font color="yellow">Did you used to work here,</font>
<font color="yellow">then, Jane?</font>

34:09.040 --> 34:10.320
<font color="lime">I was a patient.</font>

34:12.440 --> 34:14.320
<font color="lime">And then I became a trustee.</font>

34:16.639 --> 34:18.280
<font color="lime">I met Sister Julienne here.</font>

34:19.920 --> 34:21.480
<font color="lime">She's been very kind to me.</font>

34:29.719 --> 34:32.000
<font color="yellow">I won't say anything to the others.</font>

34:36.840 --> 34:39.080
<font color="yellow">Jane, would you say</font>
<font color="yellow">this is an adequate place</font>

34:39.080 --> 34:40.400
<font color="yellow">for a child to grow up?</font>

34:43.840 --> 34:45.760
<font color="lime">They would do their best.</font>

34:48.679 --> 34:51.880
<font color="white">Well, it's been many years</font>
<font color="white">since I attended a dance.</font>

34:51.880 --> 34:53.679
<font color="yellow">Oh, but you must, Reverend.</font>

34:53.679 --> 34:56.080
<font color="yellow">I couldn't bear</font>
<font color="yellow">to see these go to waste.</font>

34:56.080 --> 34:57.880
<font color="yellow">I bet you're a wonderful dancer.</font>

34:57.880 --> 34:59.200
<font color="white">LAUGHING: Oh, yes!</font>

34:59.200 --> 35:00.600
<font color="white">Quite the opposite.</font>

35:00.600 --> 35:03.080
<font color="cyan">What a perfect opportunity</font>
<font color="cyan">to learn, then.</font>

35:04.920 --> 35:07.360
<font color="lime">I'm sure Jane would enjoy herself.</font>

35:07.360 --> 35:10.320
<font color="yellow">In fact,</font>
<font color="yellow">I've got the perfect dress for her!</font>

35:11.680 --> 35:13.320
<font color="white">Ah, well.</font>

35:13.320 --> 35:17.080
<font color="white">I must confess, it will be</font>
<font color="white">a wonderful way to spend the evening.</font>

35:17.080 --> 35:18.720
<font color="white">Is Jane agreed?</font>

35:28.080 --> 35:29.600
<font color="lime">Why me?</font>

35:29.600 --> 35:31.000
<font color="white">Erm...</font>

35:31.000 --> 35:33.960
<font color="white">Well, you work so hard.</font>

35:33.960 --> 35:36.360
<font color="white">And I believe it will be fun.</font>

35:36.360 --> 35:38.880
<font color="white">Although, I must confess</font>
<font color="white">to not having danced</font>

35:38.880 --> 35:41.320
<font color="white">for, oh, a number of years.</font>

35:41.320 --> 35:44.040
<font color="white">I don't imagine that</font>
<font color="white">the Waltz is de rigeur.</font>

35:47.840 --> 35:51.320
<font color="white">Although the, erm, tribesmen,</font>
<font color="white">they taught me one of their</font>

35:51.320 --> 35:53.760
<font color="white">traditional dances and, um...</font>

35:53.760 --> 35:56.040
<font color="white">I-I won't embarrass you</font>
<font color="white">with that, though.</font>

35:58.080 --> 35:59.960
<font color="white">I'm sorry.</font>

35:59.960 --> 36:02.360
<font color="white">Please, feel free to decline,</font>

36:02.360 --> 36:04.080
<font color="white">but I would, however...</font>

36:05.480 --> 36:08.000
<font color="white">..very much like you to accompany me.</font>

36:10.360 --> 36:11.720
<font color="white">I'll stop talking now.</font>

36:19.320 --> 36:21.440
<font color="white">Though I think</font>
<font color="white">I could start talking again...</font>

36:21.440 --> 36:22.760
<font color="lime">Yes.</font>

36:25.440 --> 36:26.680
<font color="lime">Yes, thank you.</font>

36:30.440 --> 36:32.000
<font color="white">Wonderful.</font>

36:34.200 --> 36:35.560
<font color="white">Wonderful.</font>

36:57.160 --> 36:58.880
<font color="cyan">Is that Ruby's baby?</font>

37:00.120 --> 37:01.920
<font color="cyan">Or is there something</font>
<font color="cyan">you haven't told us?</font>

37:02.960 --> 37:05.600
<font color="yellow">I'm giving Mrs Roberts</font>
<font color="yellow">time to adjust.</font>

37:06.800 --> 37:10.240
<font color="cyan">We deliver the babies, Nurse Lee,</font>
<font color="cyan">we don't bring them up.</font>

37:10.240 --> 37:12.320
<font color="yellow">Sister Julienne</font>
<font color="yellow">has sanctioned my involvement.</font>

37:13.680 --> 37:15.560
<font color="white">SHE SIGHS</font>

37:35.560 --> 37:37.640
<font color="white">CHILDREN PLAYING AND SHOUTING</font>

37:37.640 --> 37:38.960
<font color="lime">Got it!</font>

37:42.600 --> 37:45.040
<font color="cyan">Oi, little 'un, is that yours?</font>

37:46.160 --> 37:48.040
<font color="cyan">Well, you move it, whatever it is.</font>

38:02.960 --> 38:05.600
<font color="white">I thought you were Douglas.</font>

38:05.600 --> 38:07.880
<font color="white">It's not like him</font>
<font color="white">to not be back by now.</font>

38:11.000 --> 38:12.360
<font color="yellow">Walk with us, Ruby.</font>

38:15.200 --> 38:18.760
<font color="white">I-I'm not up to it Nurse, please.</font>

38:20.520 --> 38:22.440
<font color="white">I'm trying, I really am.</font>

38:22.440 --> 38:24.440
<font color="white">What with Douglas</font>
<font color="white">behaving the way he is,</font>

38:24.440 --> 38:26.840
<font color="white">I'm just beside myself with worry.</font>

38:37.000 --> 38:39.200
<font color="yellow">I can't do this for ever, Ruby.</font>

38:40.800 --> 38:42.200
<font color="yellow">You have to make headway.</font>

38:44.240 --> 38:46.080
<font color="yellow">Just a little for now?</font>

38:50.360 --> 38:53.920
<font color="yellow">All I'm asking</font>
<font color="yellow">is that you walk with us.</font>

38:56.640 --> 38:58.120
<font color="yellow">Please?</font>

39:17.360 --> 39:20.680
<font color="cyan">I do believe you may have left</font>
<font color="cyan">your baby outside, Ruby, dear.</font>

39:20.680 --> 39:22.800
<font color="cyan">Not that anyone</font>
<font color="cyan">would want to steal a cripple.</font>

39:22.800 --> 39:24.080
<font color="white">Get away.</font>

39:24.080 --> 39:26.080
<font color="cyan">Wondered why we hadn't seen you</font>
<font color="cyan">for a while.</font>

39:26.080 --> 39:27.800
<font color="yellow">Come on, Mrs Roberts, we must dash.</font>

39:27.800 --> 39:29.720
<font color="cyan">Oh, she's got her own nurse,</font>
<font color="cyan">as well.</font>

39:33.080 --> 39:35.120
<font color="cyan">Not so high and mighty now, is she?</font>

39:39.920 --> 39:42.440
<font color="white">MUSIC PLAYS FROM INSIDE</font>

40:07.760 --> 40:10.440
<font color="white">WOLF WHISTLES</font>
<font color="yellow">Hello, darling! </font><font color="lime">Where you been?</font>

40:10.440 --> 40:12.320
<font color="yellow">Look, she's going inside.</font>
<font color="yellow">Come on, hurry up!</font>

40:12.320 --> 40:13.720
<font color="white">You got your comb on you...?</font>

40:13.720 --> 40:14.800
<font color="cyan">Ladies.</font>

40:14.800 --> 40:15.960
<font color="yellow">What did he say?</font>

40:15.960 --> 40:19.320
<font color="cyan">I know women who spend less time</font>
<font color="cyan">on their hair than you lot.</font>

40:19.320 --> 40:21.280
<font color="cyan">Now, get out my way.</font>

40:21.280 --> 40:22.920
<font color="yellow">Oi! Drunken idiot! </font><font color="cyan">What?</font>

40:26.880 --> 40:29.160
<font color="yellow">Hold him up!</font>
<font color="lime">Yeah, this'll teach you!</font>

40:29.160 --> 40:31.160
<font color="white">Leave him, leave him!</font>

40:31.160 --> 40:33.440
<font color="white">Unless you all wish</font>
<font color="white">to be tried for murder!</font>

40:35.520 --> 40:37.600
<font color="yellow">That's sobered him up a bit.</font>

40:37.600 --> 40:38.920
<font color="lime">Come on, leave him.</font>

40:40.480 --> 40:43.360
<font color="white">Oh, you poor man.</font>
<font color="white">They were like wild animals.</font>

40:44.680 --> 40:46.040
<font color="cyan">He's my flesh and blood.</font>

40:46.040 --> 40:48.160
<font color="cyan">She's turned her back</font>
<font color="cyan">on my flesh and blood.</font>

40:48.160 --> 40:51.720
<font color="white">I believe the alcohol may work</font>
<font color="white">as an anaesthetic, in this situation.</font>

40:51.720 --> 40:54.160
<font color="white">It's a small blessing.</font>
<font color="white">Come on, up you get.</font>

41:45.720 --> 41:47.720
<font color="white">DOOR CREAKS OPEN</font>

41:50.360 --> 41:52.000
<font color="white">DOOR CLOSES</font>

41:54.440 --> 41:55.560
<font color="yellow">It's hot.</font>

42:07.320 --> 42:09.960
<font color="white">I ain't bothered what people think,</font>

42:09.960 --> 42:11.640
<font color="white">especially not Joyce.</font>

42:13.280 --> 42:15.240
<font color="white">That isn't it, Nurse.</font>

42:15.240 --> 42:17.480
<font color="white">I don't want you thinking</font>
<font color="white">that it is.</font>

42:24.440 --> 42:25.640
<font color="yellow">Then, what is it?</font>

42:34.200 --> 42:37.000
<font color="white">If I hold him, I think</font>
<font color="white">I might die with the sadness.</font>

42:47.800 --> 42:49.600
<font color="yellow">I'm sure it'll get easier.</font>

42:54.120 --> 42:55.760
<font color="yellow">Try to eat something.</font>

43:05.120 --> 43:06.520
<font color="white">Why did they save him?</font>

43:10.080 --> 43:12.880
<font color="white">Doctor said he'll be lucky</font>
<font color="white">to see his 16th</font>

43:12.880 --> 43:16.600
<font color="white">and he'll need all sorts</font>
<font color="white">of looking after till then, so...</font>

43:16.600 --> 43:18.120
<font color="white">why did they save him?</font>

43:22.520 --> 43:23.960
<font color="yellow">Life is never without hope.</font>

43:38.480 --> 43:40.040
<font color="cyan">This is wonderful news.</font>

43:40.040 --> 43:42.360
<font color="cyan">Your parish</font>
<font color="cyan">must be eager to meet you.</font>

43:42.360 --> 43:44.520
<font color="white">Absolutely, yes, it's a...</font>

43:44.520 --> 43:47.280
<font color="white">It's a blessing that the building</font>
<font color="white">was completed so quickly.</font>

43:49.080 --> 43:51.800
<font color="cyan">Nurse Lee,</font>
<font color="cyan">if this is how you are before work,</font>

43:51.800 --> 43:54.640
<font color="cyan">I'll be interested to see</font>
<font color="cyan">what state you return in.</font>

43:56.240 --> 43:58.600
<font color="yellow">Sorry, Sister,</font>
<font color="yellow">didn't sleep too well.</font>

43:58.600 --> 44:00.160
<font color="cyan">May God give you strength.</font>

44:03.160 --> 44:05.760
<font color="lime">Enough to put you off</font>
<font color="lime">having children, eh?</font>

44:05.760 --> 44:07.960
<font color="lime">Working nights, too?</font>

44:07.960 --> 44:09.960
<font color="lime">I hope the Roberts pay well.</font>

44:09.960 --> 44:12.600
<font color="yellow">It's just until</font>
<font color="yellow">the parents come round.</font>

44:12.600 --> 44:15.120
<font color="lime">How's that little miracle</font>
<font color="lime">going to happen?</font>

44:15.120 --> 44:19.680
<font color="lime">Hmm? And how, pray tell, is you</font>
<font color="lime">doing everything for the child</font>

44:19.680 --> 44:21.320
<font color="lime">helping the parents?</font>

44:22.800 --> 44:24.560
<font color="lime">Appeasing your own guilt, are you?</font>

44:26.760 --> 44:28.400
<font color="yellow">I have no idea what you mean.</font>

44:31.560 --> 44:34.480
<font color="lime">I saw your face</font>
<font color="lime">when that child was born.</font>

44:36.040 --> 44:41.240
<font color="lime">You were distraught, Nurse Lee, as</font>
<font color="lime">every midwife has been before you.</font>

44:41.240 --> 44:44.080
<font color="lime">God help us, we're only human.</font>

44:44.080 --> 44:47.200
<font color="lime">But your guilt</font>
<font color="lime">will not help the mother to bond.</font>

44:50.440 --> 44:51.680
<font color="yellow">What will?</font>

44:53.240 --> 44:56.120
<font color="lime">If I knew the answer to that,</font>
<font color="lime">St Gideon's would be empty.</font>

44:58.200 --> 45:01.960
<font color="lime">Sometimes, you have to admit defeat</font>

45:01.960 --> 45:04.440
<font color="lime">and let the world turn as it must.</font>

45:53.480 --> 45:54.720
<font color="yellow">Mrs Roberts?</font>

46:01.320 --> 46:02.640
<font color="cyan">What?</font>

46:03.640 --> 46:05.760
<font color="cyan">Look, we're here now. </font><font color="white">I can't.</font>

46:07.680 --> 46:09.240
<font color="cyan">We're keeping him, then?</font>

46:10.280 --> 46:11.520
<font color="white">Douglas, don't!</font>

46:16.880 --> 46:18.720
<font color="cyan">It's like a train.</font>

46:18.720 --> 46:21.320
<font color="white">When I say I can't, I can't.</font>

46:24.840 --> 46:26.200
<font color="cyan">Wait here.</font>

46:31.880 --> 46:33.320
<font color="cyan">It's just me, then.</font>

46:51.320 --> 46:53.880
<font color="yellow">Hello again, Jacob. </font><font color="lime">Hello.</font>

46:53.880 --> 46:55.880
<font color="lime">She's waiting for you.</font>

46:55.880 --> 46:57.240
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

46:58.240 --> 47:00.840
<font color="lime">Did you have a fight with King Kong?</font>

47:02.840 --> 47:04.160
<font color="cyan">What did he say?</font>

47:04.160 --> 47:06.160
<font color="yellow">Say it again, please, Jacob.</font>

47:06.160 --> 47:10.680
<font color="cyan">Did you have a fight with King Kong?</font>

47:12.040 --> 47:15.760
<font color="cyan">Oh! No, mate, just, er,</font>
<font color="cyan">half a dozen little monkeys.</font>

47:40.680 --> 47:44.320
<font color="white">It was in the silences</font>
<font color="white">at the dinner table</font>

47:44.320 --> 47:47.640
<font color="white">that I felt my parents'</font>
<font color="white">hatred for each other.</font>

47:49.160 --> 47:51.360
<font color="white">So, I grew accustomed</font>
<font color="white">to filling them.</font>

47:53.880 --> 47:57.320
<font color="white">I know it can be difficult to bear.</font>

47:57.320 --> 48:00.520
<font color="white">At boarding school</font>
<font color="white">I was often without company.</font>

48:03.840 --> 48:08.200
<font color="white">I talk, so that I won't know</font>
<font color="white">what the silence holds.</font>

48:15.320 --> 48:17.440
<font color="lime">Erm...</font>

48:19.200 --> 48:20.880
<font color="lime">I...</font>

48:25.040 --> 48:26.520
<font color="lime">No matter.</font>

48:44.200 --> 48:48.360
<font color="cyan">Sister. I didn't see you</font>
<font color="cyan">in service yesterday, or today.</font>

48:48.360 --> 48:51.720
<font color="white">I've been keeping up with my offices,</font>
<font color="white">whilst on duty, Sister.</font>

48:51.720 --> 48:53.160
<font color="cyan">Excellent.</font>

48:53.160 --> 48:55.480
<font color="cyan">Doctor Turner came by.</font>
<font color="cyan">He dropped this off.</font>

48:55.480 --> 48:59.160
<font color="cyan">He says, his sincerest apologies</font>
<font color="cyan">for being so absent-minded,</font>

48:59.160 --> 49:01.600
<font color="cyan">he's been carrying it around</font>
<font color="cyan">for weeks now.</font>

49:05.520 --> 49:06.760
<font color="cyan">It's charming.</font>

49:17.480 --> 49:20.480
<font color="white">We would ask that the parents</font>
<font color="white">visit as often as possible.</font>

49:20.480 --> 49:23.400
<font color="white">The bond needn't be broken, just</font>
<font color="white">because the baby's at St Gideon's.</font>

49:23.400 --> 49:24.600
<font color="white">JACOB: </font><font color="lime">..a cup of tea.</font>

49:31.880 --> 49:33.840
<font color="yellow">Mr Roberts, did you hear?</font>

49:35.240 --> 49:36.760
<font color="cyan">What happened to him?</font>

49:38.120 --> 49:39.840
<font color="white">He was born that way.</font>

49:41.600 --> 49:43.600
<font color="cyan">Why?</font>

49:43.600 --> 49:45.240
<font color="white">It happens.</font>

49:45.240 --> 49:48.600
<font color="white">Approximately, one in a thousand</font>
<font color="white">babies are born like Jacob, there,</font>

49:48.600 --> 49:50.440
<font color="white">or like your child.</font>

49:50.440 --> 49:51.840
<font color="cyan">A thousand to one?</font>

49:51.840 --> 49:53.320
<font color="cyan">Should've had money on it.</font>

49:57.520 --> 50:00.240
<font color="white">Thank you, Martin. And Jacob.</font>

50:04.800 --> 50:06.840
<font color="lime">It's not poisoned.</font>

50:12.960 --> 50:14.400
<font color="cyan">What's it like here?</font>

50:16.160 --> 50:19.600
<font color="lime">There's a biscuit factory next door.</font>

50:19.600 --> 50:21.040
<font color="cyan">Nice.</font>

50:22.360 --> 50:24.320
<font color="lime">We get the broken ones.</font>

50:35.360 --> 50:37.080
<font color="cyan">I need to talk to my wife.</font>

50:40.320 --> 50:41.600
<font color="yellow">My apologies.</font>

50:41.600 --> 50:43.160
<font color="yellow">Mr Roberts?</font>

50:43.160 --> 50:45.360
<font color="cyan">I know my Ruby, Nurse,</font>
<font color="cyan">and I like a gamble.</font>

50:48.960 --> 50:51.040
<font color="cyan">Right.</font>

50:51.040 --> 50:54.040
<font color="cyan">We'll get back</font>
<font color="cyan">and pack its things. </font><font color="white">What?</font>

50:55.240 --> 50:56.880
<font color="cyan">The lady says she can take it.</font>

50:56.880 --> 50:58.880
<font color="cyan">They're pushed,</font>
<font color="cyan">but they can squeeze it in.</font>

51:00.480 --> 51:03.240
<font color="cyan">It's good here, there's</font>
<font color="cyan">a biscuit factory a few doors down.</font>

51:12.440 --> 51:15.680
<font color="white">REVEREND LAUGHING AND TALKING</font>

51:34.320 --> 51:36.320
<font color="white">But the nurse was helping.</font>

51:36.320 --> 51:38.760
<font color="cyan">Well, no, she weren't supposed to.</font>

51:38.760 --> 51:42.120
<font color="cyan">She can't do that for ever, can she?</font>

51:42.120 --> 51:45.480
<font color="cyan">No, they should have taken him</font>
<font color="cyan">to the home straight away.</font>

51:46.600 --> 51:48.160
<font color="cyan">Right, is that everything?</font>

51:53.040 --> 51:55.160
<font color="cyan">I'll take this. You grab it.</font>

52:28.280 --> 52:29.720
<font color="cyan">Grab it then.</font>

52:37.480 --> 52:39.040
<font color="white">He's not an "it".</font>

52:40.320 --> 52:41.760
<font color="cyan">What?</font>

52:41.760 --> 52:44.280
<font color="white">He's not "it"! He's a baby.</font>

52:45.800 --> 52:48.520
<font color="cyan">Yeah? </font><font color="white">Yeah, he's my baby boy.</font>

52:49.960 --> 52:52.560
<font color="white">How could you</font>
<font color="white">even think to send him away?</font>

52:54.520 --> 52:56.080
<font color="cyan">Yeah.</font>

52:56.080 --> 52:57.760
<font color="cyan">What a bastard, eh?</font>

53:32.960 --> 53:35.080
<font color="cyan">Change of plan, Nurse.</font>

53:35.080 --> 53:36.480
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry?</font>

53:36.480 --> 53:41.240
<font color="white">Douglas Junior is going nowhere.</font>
<font color="white">He's staying right here, with us.</font>

53:42.960 --> 53:45.120
<font color="cyan">You look like you could do</font>
<font color="cyan">with a kip, love.</font>

53:46.480 --> 53:48.120
<font color="yellow">Are you sure she's all right?</font>

53:48.120 --> 53:50.320
<font color="cyan">We're going to be fine. Yeah.</font>

53:51.640 --> 53:55.000
<font color="yellow">'It had been the biggest gamble</font>
<font color="yellow">of Douglas Roberts's life.</font>

53:55.000 --> 53:57.080
<font color="yellow">'The stakes had been high,</font>

53:57.080 --> 54:01.680
<font color="yellow">'but the dividend paid</font>
<font color="yellow">were permanent and beautiful.'</font>

54:06.760 --> 54:08.400
<font color="lime">Reverend?</font>

54:08.400 --> 54:10.440
<font color="white">Ah, Jane, I'm so pleased you...</font>

54:10.440 --> 54:11.840
<font color="lime">It's my turn to talk.</font>

54:18.800 --> 54:21.120
<font color="lime">I've always been scared.</font>

54:21.120 --> 54:22.680
<font color="lime">As long as I can remember.</font>

54:24.440 --> 54:28.360
<font color="lime">They say I used to sit bolt upright</font>
<font color="lime">in bed and scream.</font>

54:30.480 --> 54:31.760
<font color="lime">My parents sent me away.</font>

54:33.440 --> 54:36.880
<font color="lime">I don't blame them,</font>
<font color="lime">but for a long time, I was...</font>

54:38.680 --> 54:40.160
<font color="lime">..away.</font>

54:45.120 --> 54:48.520
<font color="lime">Your stories about Africa are like</font>
<font color="lime">the picture books brought to life,</font>

54:48.520 --> 54:51.280
<font color="lime">and the way you saved that man</font>
<font color="lime">outside the dance hall...</font>

54:51.280 --> 54:53.280
<font color="white">Oh, you were there?</font>
<font color="white">I... </font><font color="lime">Please.</font>

54:54.840 --> 54:58.280
<font color="lime">Life, for me, is full of fear,</font>

54:58.280 --> 54:59.920
<font color="lime">but I want you to know...</font>

55:01.400 --> 55:04.520
<font color="lime">..I really wanted to come</font>
<font color="lime">to the dance with you.</font>

55:04.520 --> 55:05.880
<font color="lime">I was too scared.</font>

55:07.640 --> 55:09.200
<font color="lime">I still struggle.</font>

55:11.360 --> 55:13.040
<font color="lime">So...</font>

55:14.440 --> 55:16.880
<font color="lime">..I think you deserve</font>
<font color="lime">somebody brave.</font>

55:21.800 --> 55:24.600
<font color="lime">I've grown accustomed</font>
<font color="lime">to the sound of your voice.</font>

55:25.840 --> 55:28.040
<font color="lime">It's strange</font>
<font color="lime">when you aren't talking.</font>

55:30.800 --> 55:34.760
<font color="white">You...are so brave.</font>

55:44.320 --> 55:46.400
<font color="lime">Oi! Dougie!</font>

55:46.400 --> 55:49.320
<font color="lime">Long time, old pal. Hello, Rube.</font>

55:49.320 --> 55:50.480
<font color="white">Hello, Fred.</font>

55:51.560 --> 55:55.240
<font color="yellow">'Sometimes in life,</font>
<font color="yellow">one has to take a chance.</font>

55:55.240 --> 55:58.200
<font color="yellow">'Without risk,</font>
<font color="yellow">there's no possibility.</font>

55:58.200 --> 56:00.920
<font color="yellow">'Without potential loss, no prize.'</font>

56:02.720 --> 56:05.600
<font color="lime">Hello, fella. Hey-hey!</font>

56:05.600 --> 56:07.320
<font color="lime">Blue for a boy.</font>

56:07.320 --> 56:09.680
<font color="lime">Right. </font><font color="cyan">Oh, it's all right, Fred.</font>

56:09.680 --> 56:12.040
<font color="lime">No, a bet's a bet.</font>

56:12.040 --> 56:14.120
<font color="lime">Handsome young man you got there.</font>

56:14.120 --> 56:15.880
<font color="lime">Three bob.</font>

56:15.880 --> 56:17.320
<font color="cyan">We'd better be off.</font>

56:19.760 --> 56:22.600
<font color="lime">'Ere, how about a little tickle</font>
<font color="lime">on the World Cup final?</font>

56:22.600 --> 56:25.200
<font color="lime">Double or quits?</font>
<font color="lime">Don't half fancy Sweden.</font>

56:25.200 --> 56:27.600
<font color="white">He's off the gambling, Fred.</font>

56:27.600 --> 56:28.680
<font color="lime">Yeah?</font>

56:30.200 --> 56:32.920
<font color="lime">Your loss.</font>
<font color="lime">See you around, Doug. </font><font color="cyan">Yeah.</font>

56:32.920 --> 56:36.120
<font color="yellow">'The Roberts' baby</font>
<font color="yellow">defied all odds...'</font>

56:36.120 --> 56:37.680
<font color="lime">But, Rubes! </font><font color="white">I said no!</font>

56:37.680 --> 56:41.560
<font color="yellow">'..and thrived,</font>
<font color="yellow">and was cherished...always.'</font>

56:44.640 --> 56:49.320
<font color="white">I have concluded that green potatoes</font>
<font color="white">are not the culprit.</font>

56:49.320 --> 56:51.680
<font color="cyan">And how did you reach this epiphany?</font>

56:51.680 --> 56:55.360
<font color="white">I had one yesterday</font>
<font color="white">and felt perfectly well.</font>

56:55.360 --> 56:58.800
<font color="cyan">Huh! For you to have a birth</font>
<font color="cyan">of any kind, my dear,</font>

56:58.800 --> 57:01.640
<font color="cyan">it would be a miracle</font>
<font color="cyan">surpassing that of the Virgin Mary.</font>

57:05.120 --> 57:09.520
<font color="yellow">'Jane, too,</font>
<font color="yellow">found acceptance in Nonnatus House.'</font>

57:11.680 --> 57:14.160
<font color="yellow">'And she found more -</font>
<font color="yellow">she found love.'</font>

57:16.920 --> 57:22.840
<font color="yellow">'The name of the goldfish she won</font>
<font color="yellow">at the fair provided proof of that.'</font>

57:24.480 --> 57:26.000
<font color="white">Hello, there, little one.</font>

57:27.200 --> 57:29.880
<font color="white">Hello, there,</font>
<font color="white">Reverend Applebee-Thornton.</font>

57:53.360 --> 57:56.320
<font color="white">We thought perhaps the Sisters</font>
<font color="white">could have a handicrafts stall</font>

57:56.320 --> 57:57.680
<font color="white">and organise a baby show.</font>

57:57.680 --> 57:59.120
<font color="cyan">A baby show?</font>

58:00.560 --> 58:02.040
<font color="white">CROWD CHEERING</font>

58:02.040 --> 58:03.400
<font color="yellow">Mrs Harding,</font>

58:03.400 --> 58:06.360
<font color="yellow">There's only one way you can</font>
<font color="yellow">deliberately terminate a pregnancy.</font>

58:06.360 --> 58:08.320
<font color="lime">And it's against the law.</font>

58:08.320 --> 58:09.880
<font color="cyan">That was unforgivable.</font>

58:09.880 --> 58:12.560
<font color="white">Who is it who decides what is</font>
<font color="white">forgivable and unforgivable?</font>

58:13.760 --> 58:17.040
<font color="white"># Anyhow, that's how I feel</font>

58:17.040 --> 58:19.800
<font color="white"># Wow, I feel</font>

58:19.800 --> 58:22.400
<font color="white"># Just like a Pollyanna</font>

58:22.400 --> 58:25.040
<font color="white"># I should worry</font>

58:25.040 --> 58:27.640
<font color="white"># Not for nothing</font>

58:27.640 --> 58:32.320
<font color="white"># Everybody loves me, yes, they do</font>

58:32.320 --> 58:37.240
<font color="white"># And I love everybody... #</font>

